    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"overwhelmingly\" is a pretty strong word lol. isn't there also a lot of debate about how deterrence works? like if people know the penalties are heavy, doesn't that theoretically stop them from committing crimes in the first place? what about the side that says we need more order to make neighborhoods viable again?",
